{"tid":1538771,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一個無用嘅香港人，但我有嘢想講","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T00:21:07.000Z","uid":167172,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c33350be9d8b568382a62d2eb2c35129a7743f15","tid":1538771,"uid":167172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:51:03.000Z","msg":"我係一個意志力好弱嘅人<br />\n經常都會想離開呢個世界<br />\n所以好明白義士了結生命時嗰種無力感<br />\n呢幾個月嚟我每日都迫到自己資訊疲勞<br />\n每晚都要靠安眠藥先瞓到<br />\n<br />\n好多人叫我放低吓俾自己抖吓<br />\n但我做唔到去漠視香港每日發生嘅事<br />\n有人受傷有人流血有人被補甚至犧牲...<br />\n我好攰好想放棄無貢獻嘅自己<br />\n但係一直以嚟有好多身邊甚至係陌生嘅同路人<br />\n一直一直同我行到今日<br />\n多謝可愛嘅香港人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢幾個月嚟香港人付出咁多嘢先<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">傳聞</span>話會回應一個訴求<br />\n仲有好長嘅路<br />\n希望大家唔好放棄<br />\n同我呢個無用嘅香港人繼續行落去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人加油</span>"},{"pid":"855b957bdd479885007da82ec2c3fd66ee0cb8f9","tid":1538771,"uid":167172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:04:07.000Z","msg":"我就算要死<br />\n都希望用條命為香港貢獻返啲嘢"},{"pid":"30207f22ed4a0b7a617e4e61d14244c7e4f51baf","tid":1538771,"uid":170176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:05:04.000Z","msg":"每日mon post mon到夜一夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後第二日又要一早起身番工<br />\n但愈睇就愈訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全覺得心力交瘁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我打死都唔會放棄架！！！<br />\n絲如果有需要可以support大家<br />\n我地齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9309f8efd1b6bbf2eafc836306def1976f6af1bc","tid":1538771,"uid":167172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":